  "title": "Mini Victoria Sponge Cakes",
  "subtitle": "A cake worth the weighing.",
  "excerpt": "Mini Victoria Sponge Cakes. A baking recipe from Rebecca's collection, straightforward, reliable, worth weighing rather than scooping.",
