  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Mini Victoria Sponge Cakes. A British home-cook's dish, the kind of recipe families adjust across generations. Adjustable for what you need.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Cake batters reward weighing over scooping. Room-temperature butter and eggs, raised properly, tested with a skewer.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
